\v 13 Ro pen tiham…ôkeikei mho n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôk…®miaha r…ôrer mwatuk t…® noien wok, mho n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôk…®miaha pw…ôh rukur…ôn amasan. Tih…ômri pen …ôknek…®n n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôk…®miaha ia namasanien s…ô Kumwes…ôn truvei pehe m k…®miaha n…ôp…®n tuk…ôtoni Iesu Kristo rier pehe.
\v 14 \x - \xo 1:14 \xt Rom 12:2, Efes 2:3, 4:17-18\x*Tiho n…ôkwai Kumwes…ôn r…ômwhen ia n…ôkw…ôrhakw…ôrha me s…ôm…ôme kamho n…ôkwai tata me. Fwe kupw…ôn k…®miaha hi…ôreirei nari, n…ôn…ô mamho noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôm…ôme rer…®miaha rokeikei p…®k. M…ôt…ô t…ôkwt…ôkwuni tih…ôpw…ôh n…ôseniien ia n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien me n…ôha ravi raka mwi k…®miaha.
\v 15 Kumwes…ôn s…ô r…®n…ôkwein ia k…®miaha in I…ôm…ô ikinan, in r…ômher. Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô k…®miaha mwi tiham…ôkeikei mho k…®miaha n…ôkur ikinan me, mh…ômher ia narimnari me pam s…ôm…ôme hiamo.
\v 16 \x - \xo 1:16 \xt Lev 11:44-45, Mat 5:48\x*Iakani iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô N…ôkuku…ô Ikinan rani m…ô, ‚ÄúTiham…ôkeikei mho k…®miaha n…ôkur ikinan me, mh…ômher, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô iou I…ôm…ô ikinan iak…ômher.‚Äù
