\v 17 \x - \xo 1:17 \xt Mat 6:9, Rom 2:11, 2Tim 4:14, Rev 2:23\x*K…®miaha hiam…ôkwein Kumwes…ôn m…ô ‚ÄúTata.‚Äù M…ôt…ô in Kumwes…ôn ramo r…ômn…ômwhen ia n…ôrmama me pam. Tr…ôrpw…®n noien me s…ôv…ônraha tresi pen atukwatukw n…ôfe ir…ôha h…ôno. Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô m…®ne, n…ôp…®n k…®miaha hiamar…ô ihi ia t…ôkure t…®pr…ôn…ô i, tiham…ôkeikei mhehek…®r in, mamho noien s…ô ramasan.
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt 1Kor 6:20\x*K…®miaha hi…ôukur…ôn m…ô k…®neivinari ia k…®miaha hi…ôuv…ôier raka ia nar…ôien …ôr…ôha n…ôha kaha kupw…ôn me s…ôk…®miaha h…ôm…ôuvei pehe m k…®miaha. M…ôt…ô k…®pk…ôr…ôku raka mh…ô k…®miaha ia nari riti s…ô truvehe m…ôr…ôha m…ômwhen ia kol m…®ne silva,
\v 19 \x - \xo 1:19 \xt Wok Me 20:28, Hip 9:12-14, 1Tes 1:2\x*rek…ôm. M…ôt…ô k…®n…ôr…ôku raka k…®miaha ia n…®te Kristo in n…ôri keikei ramasan p…®k. Kristo in r…ômwhen ia kw…ôti sipsip s…ô ratukwatukw pam, nemh…ôien u…ô n…ôr…ôhaien riw…ôn anan ir…ô.
\v 20 \x - \xo 1:20 \xt Wok Me 2:23, Efes 1:4\x*Kumwes…ôn ruv…ôrfi raka in fwe tui n…ôp…®n t…®pr…ôn…ô ramiw…ôn ihi, n…ôn…ô t…ôkwt…ôkwuni r…®pko mh…ô tui n…ôp…®n sampam ruvehe k…ôtoni in rier pehe masitu ia k…®miaha.
\v 21 \x - \xo 1:21 \xt Jon 14:6, Rom 4:24, 5:1-2, Rom 10:9\x*Ia Kristo k…®miaha hiam…ôni n…®p…ôrhienien ia Kumwes…ôn s…ô r…®no in r…ôtui mwi ia nemh…ôien s…ôv…ônhi n…ôn…ô muvei pen nasoriien min. Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô I…ôm…ô s…ô hiamahat…ôt…ô ir…ô, mamh…ômri pen …ôknek…®n n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôk…®miaha ir…ô, in i Kumwes…ôn.
