\v 22 \x - \xo 1:22 \xt Jon 13:34, Rom 12:10\x*K…®miaha hiamesi pen n…ô…°kiariien s…ô ro n…®p…ôrhienien mamhokeikei p…ôrhien pi…ôvtaha me. Ia noien n…ôha hi…ôn…ôp…ôrhi raka n…®m…®ruien me s…ôk…®miaha h…ômher. M…ôt…ô k…®miaha tiham…ôkeikei mh…ôr…®p…®n mamhokeikei p…ôrhien k…®miaha me ia rer…®miaha pam.
\v 23 \x - \xo 1:23 \xt Jon 1:13, Hip 4:12\x*K…®miaha hi…ôn…ôtui mwi r…ômwhen n…ôkw…ôrhakw…ôrha me, n…ôn…ô, n…®m…®ruien vi s…ô hi…ôn…ôtui mwi ir…ô r…®pkuku pen mh…ô t…® tata riti s…ô tremh…ô, m…ôt…ô ruku pen t…® Tata riti s…ô tr…®pkemh…ô mh…ô. N…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn s…ô ram…®ru mamar…ô rer…®n r…®no k…®miaha hi…ôtui mwi.
\v 24 \x - \xo 1:24 \xt Jem 1:10-11\x*Iakani iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô N…ôkuku…ô Ikinan rani m…ô,
