\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt Efes 4:22, Jem 1:21\x*Ro pen k…®miaha tiham…ôkeikei mh…ôpw…ôh noien …ôr…ôha me pam. Tih…ôpw…ôh mwi neiku…ôien, mh…ôpw…ôh mwi noien n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôk…®miaha ro k…ôru. Tih…ôpw…ôh mwi n…ômw…ôkien ia k…®miaha me, mh…ôpw…ôh mwi n…®niien n…®karemiaha me.
\v 2 \x - \xo 2:2 \xt Mat 18:3, 1Kor 3:2\x*K…®miaha tiham…ôkeikei mh…ôuvehe mhokeikei p…®k n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn s…ô r…ômher mh…ômwhen i…ôkunouihi …ômt…ômet…ô me i kamhas…ôk m…ô tuhes…®s. N…ô…°kiariien i tro k…®miaha hi…ôuvehe mh…ôpwinari, n…ôn…ô, Kumwes…ôn ruvehim…®ru k…®miaha.
