\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt Mat 21:42, Aes 28:16\x*H…ôuvehe t…® Kristo. In n…ôha k…ôru…ôterei m…®ru n…ôha n…ôrmama me h…ôni m…ô r…ôr…ôha, mh…ôpw…ôh, m…ôt…ô ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn in k…ôru…ôterei keikei anan s…ô in r…®m…ôrfi.
