\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt Aes 9:2, Aes 40:20-21, 1Tes 2:5, Taet 2:14, Wok Me 26:18, Efes 5:8\x*M…ôt…ô k…®miaha n…ôrmama ia kw…ôn…ôkwus i Kumwes…ôn r…®m…ôrfi k…®miaha, k…®miaha pris me s…ôv…ôi ki…°, k…®miaha n…ôrmama ikinan me ia kusen kuatia, k…®miaha n…ôrmama me s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn …ôpa. K…®no k…®miaha iam…®nha ir…ô m…ô k…®miaha hi…ôukur…ôn n…®ni irapwien narimnari amasan me Kumwes…ôn r…®no. In r…®n…ôkwein ia k…®miaha m…ô tiharaka ia n…ôpit…ôvien mh…ôuvehe ia nukuraanien amasan s…ôv…ônhi.
